database_schema:
CREATE TABLE `category` (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  business_id TEXT REFERENCES business(business_id),
  category_name TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE `RESTAURANT` (
  ID INT PRIMARY KEY,
  NAME TEXT,
  FOOD_TYPE TEXT,
  CITY_NAME TEXT REFERENCES GEOGRAPHIC(CITY_NAME),
  RATING REAL
);

CREATE TABLE `LOCATION` (
  RESTAURANT_ID INT PRIMARY KEY REFERENCES RESTAURANT(RESTAURANT_ID),
  HOUSE_NUMBER INT,
  STREET_NAME TEXT,
  CITY_NAME TEXT REFERENCES GEOGRAPHIC(CITY_NAME)
);

CREATE TABLE `business` (
  bid INT PRIMARY KEY,
  business_id TEXT,
  name TEXT,
  full_address TEXT,
  city TEXT,
  latitude TEXT,
  longitude TEXT,
  review_count INT,
  is_open INT,
  rating REAL,
  state TEXT
);
